Package: intronOrder
Type: Package
Title: Intron Splicing Order Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Meng", "Li", email = "limeng49631@aliyun.com", 
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Analysis of intron splicing order using ILP.
    This package implements algorithms for determining the most likely intron
    splicing order from RNA-seq data.
